WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.162 --> 00:00:09.912
一位年轻女子身着华丽的传统服装，佩戴头饰，神情严肃，周围站着持戟的卫兵。
A young woman in elaborate traditional attire with a headdress looks serious, surrounded by guards holding halberds.

2
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:18.700
夜色中，一名男子悄悄进入一个房间，他弯腰四处查看。
In the dark of night, a man quietly enters a room, bending down to look around.

3
00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:28.900
他跪下，在地面上挖掘，并藏起一些物品，随后迅速离开。
He kneels, digs in the ground, hides some items, and then quickly leaves.

4
00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:36.000
夜幕下的中式庭院，小桥流水，建筑在树木掩映中。
A Chinese garden at night, with a small bridge over water and buildings nestled among trees.

5
00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:39.400
一名身着长袍的女子从屋中走出。
A woman in a long robe emerges from the house.

6
00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:48.000
她身穿淡黄长裙和红背心，头戴花饰，款款走过小桥，然后停下四顾。
Wearing a light yellow long dress with a red vest and flowers in her hair, she gracefully crosses the small bridge, then stops and looks around.

7
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:52.000
一名男子跪在桥下，用白布遮住身体；女子看着他，神情担忧。
A man kneels under the bridge, his body covered by a white cloth; the woman looks at him with a worried expression.

8
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:56.000
男子露出头，抬头望着女子；随后，他用布将脸部遮掩。
The man peeks out, looking up at the woman; then, he covers his face with the cloth.

9
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.000
女子走出屋子，来到庭院中。
The woman walks out of the house and into the courtyard.

10
00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:03.000
她环顾四周，然后缓缓在庭院中走动。
She looks around, then slowly walks through the courtyard.

11
00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:05.000
男子从阴影中走出来，向女子靠近。
The man steps out from the shadows and approaches the woman.

12
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:09.000
女子突然转身，脸上显露出惊恐的神色。
The woman suddenly turns around, a look of terror on her face.

13
00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:14.000
她不安地站在原地，随后转身离开。
She stands still, appearing distressed, then turns and walks away.

14
00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:20.000
女子焦急地再次转身，在庭院中徘徊后，隐没入黑暗中。
The woman anxiously turns again, paces in the courtyard, and then disappears into the darkness.

15
00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:28.000
女子再次出现并走向男子，然后又恐惧地走开。
The woman reappears and walks towards the man, then walks away in fear again.

16
00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:29.400
男子跪在地上挖土，女子站在旁边看着。
The man kneels and digs in the ground, and the woman stands beside him watching.

17
00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:32.000
男子用一块白布蒙住自己的头。
The man covers his head with a white cloth.

18
00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:34.422
女子看着男子，脸上露出了微笑。
The woman looks at the man, a smile on her face.

19
00:01:35.392 --> 00:01:38.000
蒙着头的男子走到女子面前。
The man with the covered head walks up to the woman.

20
00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:40.000
女子伸出手。
The woman extends her hand.

21
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:41.000
男子接过女子手中的一个物件。
The man takes an item from the woman's hand.

22
00:01:47.492 --> 00:01:49.000
女子走向门边。
The woman walks towards the doorway.

23
00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:50.000
她转身面向男子。
She turns to face the man.

24
00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:52.000
男子从女子手中接过另一件物品，迅速藏入衣物中。
The man takes another item from the woman and quickly hides it in his clothes.

25
00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:53.000
男子跪下，开始挖土。
The man kneels down and begins to dig.

26
00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:55.000
女子注视着男子将物品埋入地下。
The woman watches as the man buries the item.

27
00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:57.000
男子起身，抓住了女子的手臂。
The man rises and grabs the woman's arm.

28
00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:58.000
女子看起来很惊讶，男子紧握着她的手。
The woman looks surprised, and the man holds her hand tightly.

29
00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:00.000
男子紧紧抱住了女子。
The man embraces the woman tightly.

30
00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:02.000
男子拉着女子进入屋里。
The man pulls the woman into the house.

31
00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:05.432
男子抱着女子跑出屋子，快速穿过花园。
The man carries the woman out of the house and quickly runs through the garden.

32
00:02:05.432 --> 00:02:07.332
男子将女子扛在肩上，继续奔跑。
The man carries the woman over his shoulder and continues to run.

33
00:02:07.332 --> 00:02:08.832
女子在男子的怀抱中拼命挣扎。
The woman struggles desperately in the man's arms.

34
00:02:08.832 --> 00:02:10.832
男子将女子抱离画面，消失在黑暗中。
The man carries the woman out of frame, disappearing into the darkness.

35
00:02:16.152 --> 00:02:27.000
旁白者再次出现，他笑着看着镜头。
The narrator reappears, smiling at the camera.